== 4. e5 ==
White takes space, closes up their position and defends their e-pawn. Black plans to attack White's pawn chain at either end, with the c-pawn and the f-pawn, but first they must prevent their knight from falling. 

Black should retreat it by playing [[/4...Nfd7|'''4...Nfd7''']]. 

[[/4...Ne4?!|'''4...Ne4?!''']] is occasionally tried, but after 5. Nxe4 dxe4 Black's pawn on e4 is permanently weak. 

